== SecureCam - Camera Security System

Author: Tyler Hyndman
Email: tyler.hyndman@gmail.com

== About

== Dependencies

Need a working web server with PHP and the program motion installed.

Documentation on montion can be found at 
<http://www.lavrsen.dk/twiki/bin/view/Motion/WebHome>

== Installation

=== Link motion.conf, threadX.conf to /etc/motion
ln /path/to/config/motion.conf /etc/motion/motion.conf
...
